            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-03/file778s0rn49k13hr8l15g.jpg?VersionId=DwI7RRrlgtbZ18L8Ojh5pUuHvgfkdxpb&amp;itok=iAGF3KS9" title="今年65岁的易纲连任中国央行掌门人。（路透社档案照）" alt="今年65岁的易纲连任中国央行掌门人。（路透社档案照）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-03/file778s0rn49k13hr8l15g.jpg?VersionId=DwI7RRrlgtbZ18L8Ojh5pUuHvgfkdxpb&amp;itok=iAGF3KS9" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
